<plot>After many weeks and months of earnest searching, Arno finds what he believes will make things right with his estranged love Julia: a tiny toy soldier made of tin. As he journeys ever closer to Julia's home, one question remains in his mind: will the sentiment and history attached to the toy soldier be enough to overcome the hurt he has caused her?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?045834</url></doc>
